gw.plugin.contact.search

Class DuplicateSearchResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.plugin.contact.search.DuplicateSearchResult

  • public class DuplicateSearchResult
extends java.lang.Object
    The result set for returning potential duplicates from the ContactSystemPlugin. Note that the Contacts returned by getPotentialDuplicates() may not be a complete representation of those Contacts in the Contact System. Check the documentation for the ContactSystemPlugin implementation to see if these Contacts are just partial Contacts to allow a user to select one from the collection.

    • Method Detail

      • getPotentialDuplicates

        public java.util.Collection<ContactMatch> getPotentialDuplicates()
        Returns the potential duplicates. Note that the returned collection is immutable: any attempt to call add() or remove() on it will throw an exception and leave the collection unmodified. Note that the Contacts in this collection may not be a complete representation of those Contacts in the Contact System. Check the documentation for the ContactSystemPlugin implementation to see if these Contacts are just partial Contacts to allow a user to select one from the collection.
        Returns:
        The potential duplicates
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - If result is isCountOnly()
